rsc / resetcounter            Resets the Status task's counters

   Format:
      ;rsc                    Resets all the counters
      ;rsc -a                 Resets all the counters
      ;rsc -f                 Resets just the fight counter
      ;rsc -i                 Resets just the interaction counter
      ;rsc -x                 Resets the xp counter
      ;rsc -q                 Resets the quest counter
      ;rsc -m                 Resets the bank and purse counters
      ;rsc -b                 Resets the bank counter
      ;rsc -p                 Resets the purse counter

   Notes:
      Multiple switches are allowed, e.g. ';rsc -f -x -q'

   User commands:
      rsc / resetcounter
